// Featured project — Giffen House. SSI's affordable-housing investment arm is
// acquiring and preserving the real estate; a qualified operator (to be
// announced) will run the program. Operator names, deal figures, the seller,
// and the street address are confidential — do not add them here. Anchor
// #housing matches the header nav.
---
<section class="section cream" id="housing">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="opener">
      <div class="eyebrow">Affordable Housing Investment · Featured Project</div>
      <h2>Giffen House</h2>
      <p class="lead">Where our affordable-housing investment goes to work — preserving an existing affordable property so it stays in service for the community, for the long term.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="giffen-card">
      <div class="giffen-body">
        <p class="giffen-intro">Strategic Solutions has identified and entered negotiations to acquire <strong>Giffen House</strong>, a transitional housing property in Santa Rosa that serves low-income women, with or without children.</p>
        <p>Through our affordable-housing investment program, SSI would acquire and preserve the real estate — maintaining the property's existing affordability commitments and its role as a vital community resource, and assuming its existing public financing. Consistent with our mission, SSI's role is to own and preserve the real estate for the long term.</p>
        <p>We are interviewing qualified operating partners and expect to select an experienced local nonprofit to deliver housing and supportive services to residents under a long-term operating arrangement. The transaction is expected to close in the third quarter of 2026, subject to customary approvals and due diligence.</p>
        <p class="giffen-quote"><em>“Our goal is simple: keep this housing affordable and in service for the women and families who depend on it. We handle the real estate and preservation so that a mission-driven operator can focus entirely on serving residents.”</em><br />— Luke Monroe, Executive Director</p>
      </div>

      <aside class="giffen-meta">
        <div class="giffen-stack-item">
          <div class="micro">Status</div>
          <div class="val">In negotiation · target close Q3 2026</div>
        </div>
        <div class="giffen-stack-item">
          <div class="micro">Program</div>
          <div class="val">Affordable Housing Investment</div>
        </div>
        <div class="giffen-stack-item">
          <div class="micro">Commitment</div>
          <div class="val">Housing for women & children</div>
        </div>
        <div class="giffen-stack-item">
          <div class="micro">Operating partner</div>
          <div class="val">Qualified nonprofit · to be announced</div>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
